translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: めでたしめでたし　という所だが・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: And so it ended happily... or so it seems...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 戦いの終盤、魔王美樹が覚醒しかけてしまい
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Near the end of the battle, the Demon King Miki nearly awakened,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そのせいでシィルが氷漬けになってしまった
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and because of that, Seel ended up frozen in ice.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: はにほー
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hanihoo (a greeting or catchphrase).

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 後々、関係してくる設定ポイントをまとめるよ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Let me summarize the setting points that will become relevant later.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＪＡＰＡＮを救い、ランスは救世主となる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Saving JAPAN, Rance becomes the savior.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 香姫、兄として慕われる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Kouki is admired as an older brother.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔人を１体倒す
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Defeat one demon.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: シィル、氷漬けのまま
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Seel remains frozen in ice.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 鈴女
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Suzujo.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 香姫
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Kouki.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスクエスト
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rance Quest.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ２０１１年発売
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Released in 2011.
800 x 600, Windows only.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: シィルが氷漬けのまま戻せない
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Unable to reverse Seel's frozen state.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: カラーの女王なら呪いのプロなので直せるはず
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Since the Queen of Cala is an expert in curses, she should be able to fix it.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: シィルを復活させる為の冒険を開始した
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The adventure to restore Seel's life has begun.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: コパンドンが作ったＣＩＴＹを拠点に活動…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Operating from the city built by Copandon...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ギルドでいろいろな仕事を受ける…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Taking various jobs at the guild...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: カラーの情報を集める…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Gathering information about Cala...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: なんとかカラーの村に侵入
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Somehow infiltrated Cala's village.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 女王パステルと接触するもつい犯してしまい
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Made contact with Queen Pastel but ended up assaulting her by mistake.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 怒らせてしまった
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Angered her.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 八甲田山で謙信の修業に付き合う…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Accompanying Kenshin in his training at Mount Hakkoda...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: リーザス城での幽霊事件を解決…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Resolved the ghost incident at Lizas Castle...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔人カイトを倒す…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Defeated the demon Kait.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＣＩＴＹの地上にランス城を作る…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Built Rance Castle on the surface of the city...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: マジックの風邪を治す為に翔竜山へ…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Went to Mount Shoryu to cure Magic's cold...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 指名手配クレインを捕まえる…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Caught the wanted man Crane...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: カラー村がヘルマン軍に攻められたのを助けたり…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Helped when Cala village was attacked by the Helman army...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: クルックーが法王になるのを手伝ったり…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Assisted Klucco in becoming the pope...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: マリアのお見合いを邪魔したり…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Interfered with Maria's arranged marriage...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス城に隣に出来た導く者のバベルの搭
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The Guide's Babel Tower was built next to Rance Castle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 乗り込んでアムを倒す
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Stormed it and defeated Am.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 救出した女王パステル
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rescued Queen Pastel.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: シィルの呪いを解くことが出来ない、がっかり
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Couldn't break Seel's curse; disappointing.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: はにほー
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hanihoo.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 後々、関係してくる設定ポイントをまとめるよ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Let me summarize the key setting points that will be relevant later.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: カラーの村を救い、カラーの英雄となる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Saved Cala village and became Cala's hero.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 女王パステル、ランスの事は嫌いだが
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Queen Pastel dislikes Rance,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスのとの間に娘リセットが産まれる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: but their daughter Reset is born.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＡＬ教の法王にクルックーが就任する
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Klucco is appointed pope of the AL religion.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスは影響力を持つ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rance gains influence.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔人を１体倒す
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Defeated one demon.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス城を作った
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Built Rance Castle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス９　−ヘルマン革命−
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rance 9 – Helman Revolution –

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ２０１４年発売
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Released in 2014.
1280 x 720, Windows only.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: シィルが氷漬けのまま戻せない
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Seel is still frozen and cannot be restored.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ヘルマンの秘宝なら戻せる可能性があるらしい
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It seems the Helman treasure might have the power to restore her.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 某国の王子パットンがランスの元に現れる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A prince named Patton from a certain country appears before Rance.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 国を取り戻す戦いに参加して欲しい
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: He asks Rance to join the fight to reclaim his country.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ヘルマンに侵入するチャンスだと引き受ける
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rance accepts, seeing it as a chance to infiltrate Helman.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスは小数精鋭のヘルマン解放軍を率いて
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rance leads a small elite Helman Liberation Army.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 神出鬼没のゲリラ戦法を使いヘルマン軍を各個撃破
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Using guerrilla tactics appearing unpredictably, they defeat Helman troops individually.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: フリークの魔法要塞も使ってどんどん突き進んだ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They also utilize Freak's magic fortress, advancing steadily.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 首都前面の防衛陣は、シベリア方面に迂回する事で突破して
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They bypass the capital's front defenses by detouring through the Siberian region.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: めでたしめでたし　という所だが・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: And so it ended happily... or so it seems...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 戦いの終盤、魔王美樹が覚醒しかけてしまい
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Near the end of the battle, the Demon King Miki nearly awakened,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そのせいでシィルが氷漬けになってしまった
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and because of that, Seel ended up frozen in ice.

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Let me summarize the setting points that will become relevant later.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＪＡＰＡＮを救い、ランスは救世主となる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Saving JAPAN, Rance becomes the savior.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 香姫、兄として慕われる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Kouki is admired as an older brother.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔人を１体倒す
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Defeat one demon.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: シィル、氷漬けのまま
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Seel remains frozen in ice.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 鈴女
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Suzujo.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 香姫
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Kouki.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスクエスト
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rance Quest.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ２０１１年発売
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Released in 2011.
800 x 600, Windows only.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: シィルが氷漬けのまま戻せない
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Unable to reverse Seel's frozen state.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: カラーの女王なら呪いのプロなので直せるはず
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Since the Queen of Cala is an expert in curses, she should be able to fix it.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: シィルを復活させる為の冒険を開始した
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The adventure to restore Seel's life has begun.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: コパンドンが作ったＣＩＴＹを拠点に活動…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Operating from the city built by Copandon...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ギルドでいろいろな仕事を受ける…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Taking various jobs at the guild...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: カラーの情報を集める…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Gathering information about Cala...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: なんとかカラーの村に侵入
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Somehow infiltrated Cala's village.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 女王パステルと接触するもつい犯してしまい
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Made contact with Queen Pastel but ended up assaulting her by mistake.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 怒らせてしまった
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Angered her.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 八甲田山で謙信の修業に付き合う…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Accompanying Kenshin in his training at Mount Hakkoda...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: リーザス城での幽霊事件を解決…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Resolved the ghost incident at Lizas Castle...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔人カイトを倒す…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Defeated the demon Kait.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＣＩＴＹの地上にランス城を作る…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Built Rance Castle on the surface of the city...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: マジックの風邪を治す為に翔竜山へ…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Went to Mount Shoryu to cure Magic's cold...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 指名手配クレインを捕まえる…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Caught the wanted man Crane...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: カラー村がヘルマン軍に攻められたのを助けたり…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Helped when Cala village was attacked by the Helman army...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: クルックーが法王になるのを手伝ったり…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Assisted Klucco in becoming the pope...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: マリアのお見合いを邪魔したり…
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Interfered with Maria's arranged marriage...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス城に隣に出来た導く者のバベルの搭
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The Guide's Babel Tower was built next to Rance Castle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 乗り込んでアムを倒す
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Stormed it and defeated Am.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 救出した女王パステル
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rescued Queen Pastel.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: シィルの呪いを解くことが出来ない、がっかり
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Couldn't break Seel's curse; disappointing.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: はにほー
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hanihoo.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 後々、関係してくる設定ポイントをまとめるよ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Let me summarize the key setting points that will be relevant later.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: カラーの村を救い、カラーの英雄となる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Saved Cala village and became Cala's hero.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 女王パステル、ランスの事は嫌いだが
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Queen Pastel dislikes Rance,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスのとの間に娘リセットが産まれる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: but their daughter Reset is born.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＡＬ教の法王にクルックーが就任する
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Klucco is appointed pope of the AL religion.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスは影響力を持つ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rance gains influence.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔人を１体倒す
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Defeated one demon.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス城を作った
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Built Rance Castle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス９　−ヘルマン革命−
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rance 9 – Helman Revolution –

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ２０１４年発売
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Released in 2014.
1280 x 720, Windows only.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: シィルが氷漬けのまま戻せない
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Seel is still frozen and cannot be restored.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ヘルマンの秘宝なら戻せる可能性があるらしい
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It seems the Helman treasure might have the power to restore her.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 某国の王子パットンがランスの元に現れる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A prince named Patton from a certain country appears before Rance.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 国を取り戻す戦いに参加して欲しい
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: He asks Rance to join the fight to reclaim his country.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ヘルマンに侵入するチャンスだと引き受ける
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rance accepts, seeing it as a chance to infiltrate Helman.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスは小数精鋭のヘルマン解放軍を率いて
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rance leads a small elite Helman Liberation Army.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 神出鬼没のゲリラ戦法を使いヘルマン軍を各個撃破
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Using guerrilla tactics appearing unpredictably, they defeat Helman troops individually.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: フリークの魔法要塞も使ってどんどん突き進んだ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They also utilize Freak's magic fortress, advancing steadily.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 首都前面の防衛陣は、シベリア方面に迂回する事で突破して
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They bypass the capital's front defenses by detouring through the Siberian region.
